		<article id="post-57" class="post-57 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-academic-research-and-research-papers category-college-2 category-ethics category-philosophy tag-donate-organs tag-donating-kidneys tag-donating-organs tag-kidney-black-market tag-kidney-donation tag-kidney-sale tag-legalization-of-organ-selling tag-organ tag-organ-donation tag-organ-donor tag-organ-legalization tag-organ-selling tag-sale-of-organs tag-sell-organs tag-selling-kidneys tag-selling-organs clear">
