		<div class="post-date"><a class="post-date-link" href="http://lettersfromvirginia.org/2014/04/17/legalization-of-organ-selling/" rel="bookmark">April 17, 2014</a></div><div class="post-categories"><a href="http://lettersfromvirginia.org/category/academic-research-and-research-papers/" rel="category tag">Academic Research and Research Papers</a>, <a href="http://lettersfromvirginia.org/category/college-2/" rel="category tag">college</a>, <a href="http://lettersfromvirginia.org/category/ethics/" rel="category tag">Ethics</a>, <a href="http://lettersfromvirginia.org/category/philosophy/" rel="category tag">Philosophy</a></div>	</div><!-- .post-data -->

